{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Play solo or with friends</strong></h2><br><i>Turbo Champ</i> is a fast-paced, arcade racing game. Unlock unique cars in the single-player campaign mode or play local matches with your friends.<br><br>You can even play online via Remote Play Together for game with <strong>2-4 players</strong>!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/play_with_friends.gif?t=1711751904\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Exciting game modes</strong></h2><br>Compete against friends in a classic <strong>Race</strong> game, battle over possession of a diamond in <strong>Tag</strong>, witness the questionable <strong>Bad Taxi</strong> game mode, and more! Turbo Champ has five unique game modes to choose from!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/game_modes.gif?t=1711751904\" /><br><br>You can play those games in quick matches, or in &quot;Tournament&quot; mode to prove you didn't just get lucky on that last match!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore new worlds</h2></strong><br><br>Zoom through the urban <strong>Downtown</strong>, descend the snowy <strong>Mountain</strong>, or zip through a lush <strong>Forest </strong>map. There are also battles to see in the Castle map, and new technology to witness out in the <strong>Space</strong> map.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/unlockable_cars.gif?t=1711751904\" /><br><br>Each zone has a distinct style and <strong>unique features</strong> to keep things interesting from game to game!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\"Holy cow- I'm totally going so fast!\"","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2658140/cf7641fbdb2ff98475cd9ccd8b60d1b299dd884b.jpg"},{"name":"\"Gimme dat\"","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic